{"word":"H8398 - תֵּבֵל - têbêl - tay-bale' - Habitable part","slug":"H8398","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">תֵּבֵל</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Transliteration: </strong>têbêl"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Phonetic: </strong>tay-bale'"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Short Definition: </strong>Habitable part"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>&#x05EA;&#x05BC;&#x05D1;&#x05DC; - te&#x0302;be&#x0302;l</b> - <i>tay-bale'</i><p/>From <a href=\"#/H2986\">H2986</a>; the <i>earth</i> (as <i>moist</i> and therefore inhabited); by extension the <i>globe</i>; by implication its <i>inhabitants</i>; specifically a particular <i>land</i>, as Babylonia or Palestine: - habitable part, world."},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/H180\">H180</a>, <a href=\"#/H2981\">H2981</a>, <a href=\"#/H2986\">H2986</a>, <a href=\"#/H2988\">H2988</a>, <a href=\"#/H2989\">H2989</a>, <a href=\"#/H2990\">H2990</a>, <a href=\"#/H2991\">H2991</a>, <a href=\"#/H3104\">H3104</a>, <a href=\"#/H3105\">H3105</a>, <a href=\"#/H3106\">H3106</a>, <a href=\"#/H944\">H944</a>"}]}